cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper is about video person re-identification, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel deep architecture, which involves attention mechanisms and similarity measurement, indicating that it may belong to cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper uses machine learning techniques to optimize the model, suggesting that it may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves developing more effective distance metrics, which is a common topic in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper addresses the issue of privacy and security in video surveillance, which may suggest that it belongs to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
